3x ATK when attacking with 3+ Att. (2+Heal) at once;
4x ATK & reduces damage with 4+ linked Water Orbs
Parsed Description:
All Attribute cards ATK x3 when attacking with 3 of following orb types: Fire, Water, Wood, Light, Dark & Heart.
ATK x4, reduce damage taken by 25% when matching 4+ Water orbs.

Name: Ancient Water Spirit's Whirling Technique
In-game Description:
4x ATK & reduces damage with 7+ combos; 4x ATK when
attacking with 4+ Att., Orb move time +2 seconds
Parsed Description:
All Attribute cards ATK x4, 25% all damage reduction when reaching 7 combos.
All Attribute cards ATK x4 when attacking with 4 of following orb types: Fire, Water, Wood, Light & Dark.
Increases time limit of orb movement by 2 seconds.

Name: Ancient Wood Spirit's Magic Seal

4x ATK for Wood Att. & reduces dmg when HP is 50% or
more; ATK increases with 6+ linked Wood Orbs, up to 3x
Parsed Description:
All Attribute cards ATK x4, reduce damage taken by 35% when HP 50% or more.
All Attribute cards ATK x2 when simultaneously clearing 6 connected Wood orbs. ATK x0.5 for each additional connected orb, up to ATK x3 at 8 connected orbs.

Name: Ancient Wood Spirit's Battle Technique

All Attribute cards ATK x4, reduce damage taken by 35% when HP 50% or more.
All Attribute cards ATK x2.5 when reaching 2 Wood combos. Attack multiplier increases by 1 for each additional combo, up to ATK x3.5 when reaching 3 Wood combos.

Name: Monstrous Beast's Unwavering Stance

3.5x ATK for Balanced Type, 4x ATK when HP is
20% or less; may survive when HP is reduced to 0
Parsed Description:
Balanced Type cards ATK x3.5.
All Attribute cards ATK x4 when HP 20% or less.
While your HP is 50% or above, a single hit that normally kills you will instead leave you with 1 HP. For the consecutive hits, this skill will only affect the first hit.
